Puppet module: nfs

# Written by Tom McGonagle #
# mcgonagle@gmail.com
# Google Voice (617)229-5185
# http://www.puppetll.com


DESCRIPTION:
This module installs and manages nfs software
Standard and extended classes are available.
Decide and customize how you want to define configation files: static files, templates, infile modifications...


USAGE:
# Standard Classes 
include nfs              # Install and run nfs with standard configurations.
include nfs::disable     # Disable nfs service.
include nfs::disableboot # Disable nfs service at boot time, but don't stop if it's running.
include nfs::absent      # Remove nfs package.

DEPENDENCIES:
